title: People Holding Hands Medium Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Couple holding hands medium dark skin tone
description: Represents two people holding hands, specifically with both individuals having a medium-dark skin tone. It signifies connection, partnership, love, and support between two people.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the people holding hands emoji with medium-dark skin tone showcases two hands clasped together, rendered with Apple's characteristic glossy 3D shading and soft rounded edges. The skin tone is depicted with subtle variations in lighting, giving it a natural and warm appearance, symbolizing unity, partnership, and shared connection. This emoji is a powerful visual representation of friendship, love, or solidarity, particularly on Apple devices.
